{"tid":1365770,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[建立TG 工會] 策劃大罷工","createTime":"2019-07-25T17:47:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T10:46:00.000Z","uid":33904,"like":72,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"bd2a068131b51b25869ecbb5eae86ba76ac1885a","tid":1365770,"uid":33904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T17:47:22.000Z","msg":"一個人唔敢罷好正常，<br />\n但建立完網絡，<br />\n儲夠人數一野罷落去，<br />\n一定搞得成。<br />\n<br />\n構想係：<br />\n首先，開唔同行業既tg grp，<br />\n入grp條件係冇任何個人資料既staff card，<br />\n大家要好好保護自己身份。<br />\n<br />\n一路儲人數，儲夠人數就可以用投票系統決定點樣罷工，夠人就一定贏，而家最大問題係大家冇聯系，係唔會知夠唔夠人。"},{"pid":"6c421eed26ed906e76a81c4fb1f547aa26c526ad","tid":1365770,"uid":68667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T17:48:11.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"4588c9c5d0f7bbb1ea54015f5a1b8e267249c96b","tid":1365770,"uid":138296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T17:52:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ea58eddfdb3a58a9185d95208799c23b58b573aa","tid":1365770,"uid":113250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T17:53:58.000Z","msg":"我要罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca9d0318c1d1bb651c40ec77d76be74898488966","tid":1365770,"uid":30647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T17:54:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ee543261daa21a51af131d5689f8716e2cc095ef","tid":1365770,"uid":189961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T17:56:59.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cf34d56fd83938468e1f5da3f024ed862b0dcf5","tid":1365770,"uid":208452,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T17:59:38.000Z","msg":"PUSH <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">《生於亂世，有種責任》</span></span><br />\n唔好意思阻阻大家，我地想幫香港人出書，想收集大家意見<br />\n<br />\n出一本屬於香港人嘅自由之書<br />\n<a href=\"https://l