er2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T19:05:45.000Z","msg":"好多現有工會都係親中既得利益者控制，<br />\n你見而家到都係冇乜行動就知。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n加上個d人冇得隱藏身份，所以好多野想做都唔敢做，tg工會 好處係冇大台，大家分擔罷工後果，愈多人愈安全之餘，又可以係行動前知道有幾多人參加，可以用最低成本罷工。<br />\n<br />\n可以試下調返轉，組職左人，先變做正式既合法工會，由冇開始去做搞手既話，個個都怕會有後果。"},{"pid":"0a3bcafa34fc5116f15ac82bf7b81ded69923b38","tid":1365770,"uid":182088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T19:06:45.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99fff15ceb7c559521ec5e3d44d8a622917f4043","tid":1365770,"uid":33904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"049a911ec9fb24b28e043d47d1327a3a4b4a0b4b","tid":1365770,"uid":160964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T19:00:35.000Z","msg":"不如用Twitter"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T19:07:33.000Z","msg":"twitter 香港少人用，<br />\n想盡量user friendly少少，<br />\n有時麻煩少少，<br />\n出黎個結果會少好多人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過想問一下，<br />\n twitter搞有咩好處？<br />\n如果好重要既話，可以試下。"},{"pid":"688293a7d632653667775d496cc306c105de15b5","tid":1365770,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T19:08:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4ec17d1fde1dd1d9985b96a7341947e6d5f99ec1","tid":1365770,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"049a911ec9fb24b28e043d47d1327a3a4b4a0b4b","tid":1365770,"uid":160964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T19:00:35.000Z","msg":"不如用Twitter"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T19:08:23.000Z","msg":"好多人都無，唔普及"},{"pid":"689bb9c50347ce7fe9c01dc4a5f0177b78b8e60e","tid":1365770,"uid":33904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T19:14:21.000Z","msg":"想係聽日正式開始開grp收人前，<br />\n要多d idea，<br />\n各位有咩睇法可以講下，<br />\n好似頭先巴打提出有人偷圖入黎做25，<br />\n其實都解決到。"},{"pid":"f6d0ba1b0c6bf5035913bd0b04f8238c82a37d92","t